title: THURSDAY - Week 10 TNF preview 2020
itunes:title: THURSDAY - Week 10 TNF preview 2020
description:
Week 10 action kicks off tonight (0:19) with first place in the AFC south on the line as the Colts take on the Titans. Ravens quarterback Lamar Jackson (0:58) tells Rich Eisen why he hasn't been able to have the same success as his MVP season. We break down a couple big-time matchups this weekend as Kyler Murray and the Cardinals take on Josh Allen and the Bills (2:20), and Russell Wilson and the Seahawks travel to LA to face Jared Goff and the Rams (3:42). Takk McKinley finds a new home (4:30) and we have the latest on Christian McCaffrey and his injured shoulder (4:55)
